FireBase integration (go through this documentation) : https://docs.expo.dev/guides/using-firebase/#using-firebase-js-sdk

- need to use Firebase JS sdk to connect to fire base "npm install firebase"

- In side the firebase console create an web application where you can get the firebase configuration .
  use the configraion to connect to the fire base .
- then you can use the initialize and other calls to connect/auth details from the fire base

Spring security : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_GSHvvken2k (detailed explanation)

